  Translate the event to as many language as  you feel comfortable with. Translating both, title and description for each event.
  Add a comment of your wish for the creator.
  
  Step 2.
  The creator of the event verifies the translation and accepts it.
  
  Step 3.
  Your translation goes online and more people can participate in this event.
  
  
